{
  "texts": [
    "The survey constituted:",
    "Quantitative Metrics: Utilizing Likert-scale questions to rate usability, recommendation accuracy, visual appeal, and overall satisfaction.",
    "Qualitative Insights: Open-ended questions for users to articulate their experiences, identify perceived pain points, and suggest possible enhancements.",
    "A diverse pool of participants was curated to encompass varying travel experiences, tech-savviness, and travel preferences.",
    "This heterogeneity ensured that the feedback was representative and inclusive of different user types and use-cases."
  ]
}